OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the brightness across Counties
OL,7,FAntrim and Down during the morning.
OL,8,FThe showers could be heavy, perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd rumble of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy this evening with rain
OL,12,For showers, occasionally heavy with
OL,13,Fthe odd rumble of thunder. Most
OL,14,Fshowers clear through the night,
OL,15,Ffollowed by patchy mist and fog
OL,16,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
