OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FPatchy mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing first thing. Otherwise
OL,7,Flargely dry with sunny spells, but
OL,8,Fturning cloudier through the afternoon
OL,9,Fahead of evening rain setting in.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FFrequent showers on Tuesday, often
OL,13,Fheavy. Generally drier and brighter on
OL,14,FWednesday and Thursday, but still the
OL,15,Fodd spot of rain possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
